{"tid":1479123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[818]分享下點解要和理非","createTime":"2019-08-16T18:43:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T21:13:07.000Z","uid":25228,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"834ac7b8a81528e98f31545dbf4c5c45d0923808","tid":1479123,"uid":25228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:43:48.000Z","msg":"利申：核彈都唔割，但818和理非係最低風險<br />\n<br />\n運動可以持續到今時今日，仲有國際社會明確支持係因為我地可以係冇大台既情況下<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因時制宜</span></span>，於不同場合以不同抗爭方式去獲取最大成果。<br />\n<br />\n至於818點解一定要和理非？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">1. 做比國際社會睇</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果係呢個時勢可以和理非完成一百萬人遊行，我地係絕對可以從國際社會中收割一個更大既光環，繼續向中共施加壓力要正面回應五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">2. 塞住中共把口</span></span><br />\n<br />\n星期一港澳辦記招屈鳩抗爭者恐怖主義苗頭，我地最佳既回應方法就係以極和平同文明去完成一個示威。除咗令中共出醜之餘，亦可以話比淺黃到淺藍既人知我地可以控制到自己而唔係癲，從而凝聚返佢地支持。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">3. 令潛伏既鬼處於尷尬處境</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果勇武手足都可以達成共識和理非的話，啲鬼可以做到既野就越少。作為一隻鬼，有人煽動，佢做跟嗰個唔難。但係要自己做煽動就會好突兀，以手足既觀察力其實好易識破，某程度上可以廢咗佢武功。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">818非常關鍵，如果有咩差池係絕對會係endgame，到時真係可以返屋企訓覺</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57703a8896457af54d78587683877adc765d884b","tid":1479123,"uid":25228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:45:08.000Z","msg":"自推818"},{"pid":"57cb0c6220685b95f046986a5ff1cb704b20ec32","tid":1479123,"uid":25228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:45:18.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"59dbe8e4295fa38ebcacd94e41c76c2c1d3b0e1b","tid":1479123,"uid":292525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T00:15:58.000Z","msg":"818維園見"},{"pid":"4e27b3ea3f54f86639906a8053656e790feee2a4","tid":1479123,"uid":25228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T21:12:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d934aed3ff511b09506cfc28b0d9c01ba1e9d57","tid":1479123,"uid":25228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T21:12:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8514e504a15bf5f3391905005eef2f3affbb0fa5","tid":1479123,"uid":25228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T21:12:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad7ebb9b25fe904e9de935e3a924faf29d2d153","tid":1479123,"uid":25228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T21:13:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}